detail.name: Bardock
detail.effect:
[When Attacking] Draw 1 card.
[Awaken] (Can be activated during [Activate Main/Battle] if the conditions are met.) When your life is at 4 or less, draw 1 card. Then, flip this card over.

detail.name: Bardock
detail.effect:
[When Attacking] Draw 1 card. Then, this card gets +5000 power for the battle.
[Activate Battle][Your Turn][Once per turn] Look at the top card of your deck and use up to 1 Battle Card with 《Bardock's Crew》 in its special traits in a combo. Place the rest at the top or bottom of its owner's deck.
